<p>You have been scheduled to work at multiple new events.</p>

<% @events_and_roles.each do |event, role| %>
  <% @event, @role, @response_deadline = event, role, event.time_response_required_by %>
  <%= render 'event_details' %>
<% end %>

<p>
  <strong>*</strong> you have till such time to either accept or decline this
  event, before the system automatically marks your rostering as declined.
</p>

<p>
  You can accept or decline any of these event by visiting your
  dashboard at <%= link_to Setting.site_url, Setting.site_url %>
  (simply login and click <%= link_to 'My Dashboard', dashboard_url %>
  in the header)
</p>

<p>
  If you do not respond within the required time for an event,
  you will automatically be moved to the declined list for that
  event.
</p>

<%= render 'footer' %>